						               													<description>Mafia Cards is a party game in which you have to bluff and suspect. In Mafia: Cards, designed for 7-20 players, some players take on the roles of mafia members, while others become civilians of the criminal community. Every night the mafia kills another person, and every day the civilians have a chance to discuss the murder, choose suspects, and sentence one of them to death. Because each role is secret, you never know who is an innocent bystander and who is part of the mafia. If the mob kills enough civilians, the community will become a permanent haven for criminals, but if the civilians rid their community of the mob, they win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mafia: Cards offers 24 different character cards, as well as 55 superpower cards for a fun game. You can play as a don, a doctor, an innocent bystander, or a cunning minion. Whatever your role, play it convincingly, make your choices carefully, and trust no one.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As a gift also comes a premium subscription - 1 month, for our application, with which your game will be even cooler and more interesting.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
